get intermediate image sizes "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
============================================================================

NAME
----

get intermediate image sizes - Get the available image sizes

SYNOPSIS
--------

Get the available image sizes

USAGE
-----

` <?php get_intermediate_image_sizes(); ?> `

RETURN VALUES
-------------

 `` `(array)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   Returns a filtered array of image size strings

CHANGE LOG
----------

Since: [3.0](/Version_3.0 "Version 3.0")

SOURCE FILE
-----------

`get_intermediate_image_sizes()` is located in `wp-includes/media.php`

